<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<odoo>
    <record id="action_report_pick_ticket" model="ir.actions.report">
        <field name="name">Pick Ticket</field>
        <field name="model">sale.delivery.document</field>
        <field name="report_type">qweb-pdf</field>
        <field name="report_name">sale_delivery_wizard.report_pick_ticket</field>
        <field name="report_file">sale_delivery_wizard.report_pick_ticket</field>
        <field name="print_report_name">'Pick Ticket - %s' % (object.name or '')</field>
        <field name="binding_model_id" ref="model_sale_delivery_document"/>
        <field name="binding_type">report</field>
    </record>

    <template id="report_pick_ticket">
        <t t-call="web.html_container">
            <t t-foreach="docs" t-as="doc">
                <t t-call="web.external_layout">

                    <div class="page" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; color: #111827;">

                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <!-- ENCABEZADO -->
                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <div style="border-bottom: 2px solid #111827; padding-bottom: 9px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                            <div class="row" style="align-items: center;">
                                <div class="col-7">
                                    <h2 style="margin: 0; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: .05em; color: #4b362d; line-height: 1;">
                                        PICK TICKET
                                    </h2>
                                    <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 4px;">
                                        Documento interno de preparación de material
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="col-5 text-end">
                                    <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; font-weight: 700;">No. Documento</div>
                                    <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 900; color: #111827; line-height: 1.05;">
                                        <t t-esc="doc.name or '-'"/>
                                    </div>
                                    <div style="font-size: 8px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 3px;">
                                        Impreso:
                                        <t t-esc="context_timestamp(datetime.datetime.now()).strftime('%d/%m/%Y %H:%M')"/>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <!-- INFORMACIÓN GENERAL -->
                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <div class="row mb-2">
                            <div class="col-4">
                                <div style="border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 5px; padding: 7px; min-height: 98px;">
                                    <div style="font-weight: 800; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #374151; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; padding-bottom: 4px; margin-bottom: 5px;">
                                        Información comercial
                                    </div>

                                    <table class="table table-sm table-borderless" style="margin: 0; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.18;">
                                        <tr>
                                            <td style="width: 35%; padding: 1px 2px; font-weight: 700; color: #374151;">Pedido:</td>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px;">
                                                <t t-esc="doc.sale_order_id.name or '-'"/>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px; font-weight: 700; color: #374151;">Cliente:</td>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px;">
                                                <strong>
                                                    <t t-esc="doc.partner_id.name or '-'"/>
                                                </strong>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px; font-weight: 700; color: #374151;">Vendedor:</td>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px;">
                                                <t t-esc="doc.sale_order_id.user_id.name or '-'"/>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr t-if="doc.sale_order_id and 'client_order_ref' in doc.sale_order_id._fields and doc.sale_order_id.client_order_ref">
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px; font-weight: 700; color: #374151;">OC cliente:</td>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px;">
                                                <t t-esc="doc.sale_order_id.client_order_ref"/>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </table>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="col-4">
                                <div style="border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 5px; padding: 7px; min-height: 98px;">
                                    <div style="font-weight: 800; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #374151; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; padding-bottom: 4px; margin-bottom: 5px;">
                                        Información operativa
                                    </div>

                                    <table class="table table-sm table-borderless" style="margin: 0; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.18;">
                                        <tr>
                                            <td style="width: 40%; padding: 1px 2px; font-weight: 700; color: #374151;">Fecha:</td>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px;">
                                                <t t-esc="doc.create_date" t-options="{'widget': 'datetime'}"/>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px; font-weight: 700; color: #374151;">Estado:</td>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px;">
                                                <span style="font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;">
                                                    <t t-esc="dict(doc._fields['state'].selection).get(doc.state) or doc.state or '-'"/>
                                                </span>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr t-if="doc.sale_order_id and 'commitment_date' in doc.sale_order_id._fields and doc.sale_order_id.commitment_date">
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px; font-weight: 700; color: #374151;">Compromiso:</td>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px;">
                                                <span t-field="doc.sale_order_id.commitment_date" t-options='{"widget": "date"}'/>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr t-if="doc.sale_order_id and 'x_project_id' in doc.sale_order_id._fields and doc.sale_order_id.x_project_id">
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px; font-weight: 700; color: #374151;">Proyecto:</td>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px;">
                                                <span t-field="doc.sale_order_id.x_project_id.name"/>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </table>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="col-4">
                                <div style="border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 5px; padding: 7px; min-height: 98px;">
                                    <div style="font-weight: 800; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #374151; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; padding-bottom: 4px; margin-bottom: 5px;">
                                        Dirección de entrega
                                    </div>

                                    <div style="font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.18; color: #374151;">
                                        <t t-if="doc.delivery_address">
                                            <t t-esc="doc.delivery_address"/>
                                        </t>
                                        <t t-else="">
                                            <span style="font-style: italic; color: #6b7280;">Sin dirección capturada.</span>
                                        </t>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <!-- INSTRUCCIONES ESPECIALES -->
                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <t t-if="doc.special_instructions">
                            <div style="border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; background: #fffbeb; padding: 7px 9px; margin: 7px 0 9px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.18;">
                                <strong>Instrucciones especiales:</strong>
                                <span t-esc="doc.special_instructions"/>
                            </div>
                        </t>

                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <!-- DETALLE DE MATERIAL -->
                        <!-- Solo esta sección usa 10px -->
                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <div style="font-weight: 800; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 8px 0 4px; color: #111827;">
                            Materiales a preparar
                        </div>

                        <t t-set="m2_lines" t-value="doc.line_ids.filtered(lambda l: l.product_id and l.product_id.uom_id and (('m²' in (l.product_id.uom_id.name or '').lower()) or ('m2' in (l.product_id.uom_id.name or '').lower()) or ('cuadr' in (l.product_id.uom_id.name or '').lower())))"/>
                        <t t-set="unit_lines" t-value="doc.line_ids - m2_lines"/>

                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <!-- PRODUCTOS MEDIDOS EN M² -->
                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <t t-if="m2_lines">
                            <div style="font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 6px 0 3px; color: #374151;">
                                Productos medidos en m²
                            </div>

                            <table class="table table-sm table-striped" style="width: 100%; font-size: 10px; border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid #9ca3af; margin-bottom: 6px;">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr style="background-color: #111827;">
                                        <th class="text-center" style="width: 4%; padding: 2px 2px; line-height: 1; color: #ffffff !important; background-color: #111827 !important; font-weight: 800;">#</th>
                                        <th style="width: 15%; padding: 2px 2px; line-height: 1; color: #ffffff !important; background-color: #111827 !important; font-weight: 800;">LOTE</th>
                                        <th style="width: 30%; padding: 2px 2px; line-height: 1; color: #ffffff !important; background-color: #111827 !important; font-weight: 800;">BLOQUE</th>
                                        <th style="width: 22%; padding: 2px 2px; line-height: 1; color: #ffffff !important; background-color: #111827 !important; font-weight: 800;">UBICACIÓN</th>
                                        <th class="text-center" style="width: 23%; padding: 2px 2px; line-height: 1; color: #ffffff !important; background-color: #111827 !important; font-weight: 800;">
                                            ANCHO X ALTO = M²
                                        </th>
                                        <th class="text-center" style="width: 6%; padding: 2px 2px; line-height: 1; color: #ffffff !important; background-color: #111827 !important; font-weight: 800;">OK</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>

                                <tbody style="font-size: 10px; line-height: 1; border-bottom: 1px solid #111827;">
                                    <t t-set="idx_m2" t-value="0"/>
                                    <t t-set="grand_total_m2" t-value="0.0"/>
                                    <t t-set="last_product_id_m2" t-value="False"/>

                                    <t t-foreach="m2_lines.sorted(key=lambda l: ((l.product_id.display_name or ''), (l.lot_id.name or '')))" t-as="line">

                                        <t t-if="last_product_id_m2 != line.product_id.id">
                                            <tr style="background-color: #2f2f2f;">
                                                <td colspan="6" style="padding: 2px 4px; line-height: 1; font-weight: 800; font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #ffffff !important; background-color: #2f2f2f !important;">
                                                    <span t-esc="line.product_id.display_name or '-'"/>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <t t-set="last_product_id_m2" t-value="line.product_id.id"/>
                                        </t>

                                        <t t-set="idx_m2" t-value="idx_m2 + 1"/>
                                        <t t-set="qty_to_show" t-value="(('qty_selected' in line._fields and line.qty_selected) or ('quantity' in line._fields and line.quantity) or 0.0)"/>
                                        <t t-set="grand_total_m2" t-value="grand_total_m2 + qty_to_show"/>

                                        <t t-set="lot_block" t-value="line.lot_id and (('x_bloque' in line.lot_id._fields and line.lot_id.x_bloque) or ('lot_general' in line.lot_id._fields and line.lot_id.lot_general) or '') or ''"/>
                                        <t t-set="lot_width" t-value="line.lot_id and (('x_ancho' in line.lot_id._fields and line.lot_id.x_ancho) or ('marble_width' in line.lot_id._fields and line.lot_id.marble_width) or 0.0) or 0.0"/>
                                        <t t-set="lot_height" t-value="line.lot_id and (('x_alto' in line.lot_id._fields and line.lot_id.x_alto) or ('marble_height' in line.lot_id._fields and line.lot_id.marble_height) or 0.0) or 0.0"/>

                                        <tr>
                                            <td class="text-center align-middle" style="padding: 1px 2px; line-height: 1; border: 1px solid #d1d5db;">
                                                <t t-esc="idx_m2"/>
                                            </td>

                                            <td class="align-middle" style="padding: 1px 2px; line-height: 1; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; font-family: monospace; font-weight: 400;">
                                                <t t-if="line.lot_id">
                                                    <t t-esc="line.lot_id.name"/>
                                                </t>
                                                <t t-else="">
                                                    <span style="color: #6b7280; font-style: italic;">Sin lote</span>
                                                </t>
                                            </td>

                                            <td class="align-middle" style="padding: 1px 2px; line-height: 1; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; font-weight: 400;">
                                                <t t-if="lot_block">
                                                    <t t-esc="lot_block"/>
                                                </t>
                                                <t t-else="">-</t>
                                            </td>

                                            <td class="align-middle" style="padding: 1px 2px; line-height: 1; border: 1px solid #d1d5db;">
                                                <t t-esc="line._format_short_location()"/>
                                            </td>

                                            <td class="text-center align-middle" style="padding: 1px 2px; line-height: 1; border: 1px solid #d1d5db;">
                                                <t t-if="lot_width and lot_height">
                                                    <span t-esc="'%.3f x %.3f = %.2f' % (lot_width, lot_height, qty_to_show)"/>
                                                </t>
                                                <t t-else="">
                                                    <span t-esc="'%.2f' % (qty_to_show or 0.0)"/>
                                                </t>
                                            </td>

                                            <td class="text-center align-middle" style="padding: 1px 2px; line-height: 1; border: 1px solid #d1d5db;">
                                                <span style="font-size: 10px; line-height: 1;">☐</span>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </t>
                                </tbody>

                                <tfoot style="border-top: 2px solid #111827; background-color: #f3f4f6;">
                                    <tr>
                                        <td colspan="4" class="text-end" style="padding: 2px 3px; line-height: 1; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800;">
                                            TOTAL M² PREPARADO:
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="text-center" style="padding: 2px 3px; line-height: 1; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800;">
                                            <span t-esc="'%.2f' % (grand_total_m2 or 0.0)"/>
                                        </td>
                                        <td></td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tfoot>
                            </table>
                        </t>

                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <!-- PRODUCTOS MEDIDOS POR UNIDAD -->
                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <t t-if="unit_lines">
                            <div style="font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 6px 0 3px; color: #374151;">
                                Productos medidos por unidad
                            </div>

                            <table class="table table-sm table-striped" style="width: 100%; font-size: 10px; border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid #9ca3af;">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr style="background-color: #111827;">
                                        <th class="text-center" style="width: 4%; padding: 2px 2px; line-height: 1; color: #ffffff !important; background-color: #111827 !important; font-weight: 800;">#</th>
                                        <th style="width: 16%; padding: 2px 2px; line-height: 1; color: #ffffff !important; background-color: #111827 !important; font-weight: 800;">LOTE</th>
                                        <th style="width: 32%; padding: 2px 2px; line-height: 1; color: #ffffff !important; background-color: #111827 !important; font-weight: 800;">BLOQUE</th>
                                        <th style="width: 25%; padding: 2px 2px; line-height: 1; color: #ffffff !important; background-color: #111827 !important; font-weight: 800;">UBICACIÓN</th>
                                        <th class="text-center" style="width: 17%; padding: 2px 2px; line-height: 1; color: #ffffff !important; background-color: #111827 !important; font-weight: 800;">
                                            CANTIDAD
                                        </th>
                                        <th class="text-center" style="width: 6%; padding: 2px 2px; line-height: 1; color: #ffffff !important; background-color: #111827 !important; font-weight: 800;">OK</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>

                                <tbody style="font-size: 10px; line-height: 1; border-bottom: 1px solid #111827;">
                                    <t t-set="idx_unit" t-value="0"/>
                                    <t t-set="grand_total_units" t-value="0.0"/>
                                    <t t-set="last_product_id_unit" t-value="False"/>

                                    <t t-foreach="unit_lines.sorted(key=lambda l: ((l.product_id.display_name or ''), (l.lot_id.name or '')))" t-as="line">

                                        <t t-if="last_product_id_unit != line.product_id.id">
                                            <tr style="background-color: #2f2f2f;">
                                                <td colspan="6" style="padding: 2px 4px; line-height: 1; font-weight: 800; font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #ffffff !important; background-color: #2f2f2f !important;">
                                                    <span t-esc="line.product_id.display_name or '-'"/>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <t t-set="last_product_id_unit" t-value="line.product_id.id"/>
                                        </t>

                                        <t t-set="idx_unit" t-value="idx_unit + 1"/>
                                        <t t-set="qty_to_show" t-value="(('qty_selected' in line._fields and line.qty_selected) or ('quantity' in line._fields and line.quantity) or 0.0)"/>
                                        <t t-set="grand_total_units" t-value="grand_total_units + qty_to_show"/>

                                        <t t-set="lot_block" t-value="line.lot_id and (('x_bloque' in line.lot_id._fields and line.lot_id.x_bloque) or ('lot_general' in line.lot_id._fields and line.lot_id.lot_general) or '') or ''"/>
                                        <t t-set="uom_name" t-value="line.product_id.uom_id.name or ''"/>

                                        <tr>
                                            <td class="text-center align-middle" style="padding: 1px 2px; line-height: 1; border: 1px solid #d1d5db;">
                                                <t t-esc="idx_unit"/>
                                            </td>

                                            <td class="align-middle" style="padding: 1px 2px; line-height: 1; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; font-family: monospace; font-weight: 400;">
                                                <t t-if="line.lot_id">
                                                    <t t-esc="line.lot_id.name"/>
                                                </t>
                                                <t t-else="">
                                                    <span style="color: #6b7280; font-style: italic;">Sin lote</span>
                                                </t>
                                            </td>

                                            <td class="align-middle" style="padding: 1px 2px; line-height: 1; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; font-weight: 400;">
                                                <t t-if="lot_block">
                                                    <t t-esc="lot_block"/>
                                                </t>
                                                <t t-else="">-</t>
                                            </td>

                                            <td class="align-middle" style="padding: 1px 2px; line-height: 1; border: 1px solid #d1d5db;">
                                                <t t-esc="line._format_short_location()"/>
                                            </td>

                                            <td class="text-center align-middle" style="padding: 1px 2px; line-height: 1; border: 1px solid #d1d5db;">
                                                <span t-esc="'%.2f %s' % (qty_to_show or 0.0, uom_name)"/>
                                            </td>

                                            <td class="text-center align-middle" style="padding: 1px 2px; line-height: 1; border: 1px solid #d1d5db;">
                                                <span style="font-size: 10px; line-height: 1;">☐</span>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </t>
                                </tbody>

                                <tfoot style="border-top: 2px solid #111827; background-color: #f3f4f6;">
                                    <tr>
                                        <td colspan="4" class="text-end" style="padding: 2px 3px; line-height: 1; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800;">
                                            TOTAL UNIDADES PREPARADAS:
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="text-center" style="padding: 2px 3px; line-height: 1; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800;">
                                            <span t-esc="'%.2f' % (grand_total_units or 0.0)"/>
                                        </td>
                                        <td></td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tfoot>
                            </table>
                        </t>

                        <t t-if="not doc.line_ids">
                            <div style="border: 1px solid #d1d5db; padding: 8px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 11px; font-style: italic; text-align: center;">
                                Sin líneas de material para preparar.
                            </div>
                        </t>

                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <!-- ESPECIFICACIONES DE ENTREGA -->
                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <div class="row mt-2">
                            <div class="col-12">
                                <div style="border: 1px solid #111827; border-radius: 4px; padding: 6px 8px;">
                                    <div style="font-weight: 800; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 1px solid #d1d5db; padding-bottom: 3px; margin-bottom: 4px;">
                                        Especificaciones de la entrega
                                    </div>

                                    <table class="table table-sm table-borderless" style="width: 100%; margin: 0; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.18;">
                                        <tr>
                                            <td style="width: 18%; padding: 1px 2px; font-weight: 800;">Dirección:</td>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px;">
                                                <t t-esc="doc.delivery_address or '-'"/>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px; font-weight: 800;">Instrucciones:</td>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px;">
                                                <t t-esc="doc.special_instructions or 'Sin instrucciones especiales.'"/>
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px; font-weight: 800;">Validación:</td>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px;">
                                                Verificar lote, bloque, ubicación, dimensiones, cantidad física, estado visual del material y coincidencia contra el pedido antes de liberar salida.
                                            </td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px; font-weight: 800;">Observaciones:</td>
                                            <td style="padding: 1px 2px; border-bottom: 1px solid #d1d5db; height: 18px;"></td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </table>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <!-- TÉRMINOS Y CONDICIONES -->
                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <div class="row mt-2">
                            <div class="col-12">
                                <div style="border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 4px; padding: 6px 8px;">
                                    <div style="font-weight: 800; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #374151; margin-bottom: 3px;">
                                        Términos y condiciones operativas
                                    </div>

                                    <ol style="margin: 0; padding-left: 16px; font-size: 9px; line-height: 1.12; color: #374151;">
                                        <li>Este documento es de uso interno para preparación de material; no sustituye factura, remisión ni comprobante fiscal.</li>
                                        <li>El almacén debe preparar únicamente los lotes indicados en este Pick Ticket, respetando lote, bloque, ubicación, dimensiones y cantidad solicitada.</li>
                                        <li>Cualquier diferencia física, daño, faltante, ubicación incorrecta o cambio de lote debe reportarse antes de autorizar la salida.</li>
                                        <li>La casilla de verificación debe marcarse únicamente después de validar físicamente cada lote contra el material preparado.</li>
                                        <li>Si el material requiere maniobra especial, empaque, protección, flejado o equipo de carga, debe registrarse en observaciones antes de liberar entrega.</li>
                                        <li>La salida del material requiere revisión de almacén y autorización interna. No debe liberarse material con información incompleta o inconsistente.</li>
                                        <li>Las condiciones comerciales, pagos, descuentos, cambios, devoluciones o garantías se rigen por el pedido de venta y los acuerdos vigentes con el cliente.</li>
                                        <li>El responsable de preparación confirma que el material listado fue localizado, revisado y dejado listo para el siguiente paso operativo.</li>
                                    </ol>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <!-- FIRMAS -->
                        <!-- ===================================================== -->
                        <div class="row mt-3">
                            <div class="col-4 text-center">
